the person if he would take to God,

00:10:44.788 --> 00:10:48.493
if he would take to righteous life
or to something higher.

00:10:48.694 --> 00:10:52.476
And if they saw these qualities in their
child they used to be happy,

00:10:52.677 --> 00:10:57.353
but these days the other way round,
the parents don't like it.

00:10:58.839 --> 00:11:02.393
As if the parents have lost everything
in themselves,

00:11:02.594 --> 00:11:07.914
so they want to hold on to their children,
grandchildren and possess them.

00:11:08.603 --> 00:11:12.146
And brainless creatures, because their
brain has been already washed out,

00:11:12.347 --> 00:11:18.104
there's nothing in their brains. To fight
the parents also is a big problem.

00:11:18.305 --> 00:11:22.005
So this kind of a fear is also there, that:
"My mother should not know,

00:11:22.206 --> 00:11:26.072
my father should not know," this, that.

00:11:26.844 --> 00:11:30.178
You can say from all sides

00:11:31.830 --> 00:11:37.616
the fear is burning, like flames.

00:11:37.817 --> 00:11:45.099
And we are now here, in Kali Yuga, we have
started Sahaja Yoga.

00:11:48.037 --> 00:11:57.329
So the way we have to work out
our protection has to be mutual.

00:11:57.530 --> 00:12:04.231
Mother of course is there to protect you
all the time,

00:12:04.432 --> 00:12:07.620
Her powers are there to protect you.

00:12:07.821 --> 00:12:12.312
But surprisingly in the modern times,

00:12:12.513 --> 00:12:17.349
there's one condition which has to be
fulfilled.

00:12:19.159 --> 00:12:24.504
Because in those days good were good

00:12:24.705 --> 00:12:29.725
and evil were evil, there was no mixing up.

00:12:30.434 --> 00:12:33.358
So once they asked for Goddess, they
accepted Her,

00:12:33.559 --> 00:12:36.946
She came in Her real form and She worked
it out.

00:12:37.147 --> 00:12:42.067
But in modern times, you must know that
all these evil things

00:12:42.268 --> 00:12:46.576
are also lingering in your head, little bit
here and there.

00:12:46.777 --> 00:12:49.191
People are extremely superficial,

00:12:49.392 --> 00:12:56.589
they are very much prone to the mass
attitude, fashions, things like that.

00:12:56.790 --> 00:13:01.794
Sort of, their personality is not that
developed as that

00:13:01.995 --> 00:13:06.494
of those bhaktas who knew they were right,
who knew they were righteous,

00:13:06.695 --> 00:13:08.744
who knew whatever they were doing
was correct

00:13:08.945 --> 00:13:15.895
and were standing on their legs firm.

00:13:16.096 --> 00:13:24.908
So the modern Sahaja Yogi is very different
from the Sahaja Yogi of olden times.

00:13:25.109 --> 00:13:31.654
Because in the olden times it was not easy
to get Realization.

00:13:31.950 --> 00:13:36.756
One in a billion, or in a trillion.

00:13:38.122 --> 00:13:42.850
And they had to work very hard, so as they
worked hard, very hard,

00:13:43.051 --> 00:13:47.876
they got cleansed and built up themselves,
you see, and toiled.

00:13:48.077 --> 00:13:52.811
Like any art piece which takes time,
is done with care,

00:13:52.982 --> 00:13:56.076
is definitely thousand times better than
these modern artists

00:13:56.277 --> 00:13:59.033
just putting two, three lines like this.

00:13:59.234 --> 00:14:03.529
So the today's human being is like a modern
artist, you see.

00:14:03.730 --> 00:14:07.286
You put one line and you say: "You must
see this into that person,

00:14:07.487 --> 00:14:10.808
you must have an identity." I mean,
what identity people can have?

00:14:11.009 --> 00:14:15.494
With one line, you say, find out
the identity.

00:14:18.025 --> 00:14:22.647
So the Sahaja Yogis which are today here,
have to realize

00:14:22.848 --> 00:14:30.218
that all these things are surrounding us,
and these evil forces are also there.

00:14:30.419 --> 00:14:34.667
There are some within us, some are without.

00:14:35.256 --> 00:14:40.730
So it's a - looks to be very difficult
task, but it's not.

00:14:43.304 --> 00:14:48.413
Because one condition if you can
understand,

00:14:49.828 --> 00:14:53.219
is that you have to recognize Me.

00:14:53.428 --> 00:14:58.637
I know I am Mahamaya, I'm really very
clever at it.

00:15:04.431 --> 00:15:10.714
But I am truthful, I do not have crocodile
tears, I cannot have.

00:15:11.081 --> 00:15:16.694
I am truthful, but still I am Mahamaya.

00:15:16.895 --> 00:15:22.189
So to recognize Me what should we do?

00:15:23.088 --> 00:15:27.629
If we recognize then you are protected.

00:15:30.416 --> 00:15:37.752
And the cleansing is the simplest thing
in Sahaja Yoga is to be collective.

00:15:37.953 --> 00:15:44.116
If you are not collective then know that
something wrong with you.

00:15:44.443 --> 00:15:50.558
If you are collective then as if you are
taking your bath in the river Ganges.

00:15:50.759 --> 00:15:54.580
You don't have to go to Himalayas, you
don't have to do individual sadhana much,

00:15:54.781 --> 00:15:57.895
you don't have to... just be collective.
If you are collective,

00:15:58.096 --> 00:16:04.303
if you are enjoying the collective, then
you should know that you are clean.

00:16:04.504 --> 00:16:10.388
No blemishes there, you are absolutely
all right.

00:16:12.445 --> 00:16:17.427
Now the second part of is - this Mahamaya
business.

00:16:17.627 --> 00:16:22.123
I had to be very close to you, I had to be
extremely close,

00:16:22.324 --> 00:16:26.582
talk to you, to have a rapport, to tell you
everything about Yoga

00:16:26.783 --> 00:16:32.602
to make you absolutely aware of yourself.
This had to be done,

00:16:32.803 --> 00:16:36.416
and with all these complications within
your mind,

00:16:36.625 --> 00:16:42.080
within your heart, within your body, I had
to work it out.

00:16:42.281 --> 00:16:49.652
To come close in the real form would have
been very dangerous,

00:16:49.853 --> 00:16:55.825
so One had to be a Mahamaya. But
despite that,

00:16:58.549 --> 00:17:05.554
if you could recognize Me,
to understand Me,

00:17:05.755 --> 00:17:12.023
that I am Divine personality,
it's an Incarnation -

00:17:12.920 --> 00:17:18.649
that's all the Deities want. Then they'll
look after you in every way.

00:17:18.850 --> 00:17:23.934
They'll give you all the powers, they'll
give you all the satisfaction,

00:17:24.135 --> 00:17:29.995
all the protection that you want. This is
the condition

00:17:30.894 --> 00:17:34.608
which for a rational mind is very difficult
to understand,

00:17:34.809 --> 00:17:40.661
that how can Adi Shakti be in one body?

00:17:41.695 --> 00:17:46.076
How can the Infinite can become finite?

00:17:47.300 --> 00:17:51.198
But human beings cannot do that.

00:17:51.882 --> 00:17:57.921
Only human beings. God can do it. He is God
after all.

00:17:59.145 --> 00:18:05.347
And if so, you have so many miracles,
you have so many photographs,

00:18:05.548 --> 00:18:11.315
so many things to see, but this is what
one has to recognize.

00:18:11.928 --> 00:18:16.676
Now I see people, when I talk to them

00:18:16.877 --> 00:18:21.872
they start talking to Me a little
frivolously,

00:18:22.073 --> 00:18:28.521
not with that depth, not with that feeling
that I am Mahamaya.

00:18:28.729 --> 00:18:33.504
Then some of them even answer Me. Some
of them, if I tell them something,

00:18:33.705 --> 00:18:39.883
they are ready to give an answer,
explanation.

00:18:40.084 --> 00:18:44.841
Of course this freedom I have given you
deliberately,

00:18:45.906 --> 00:18:53.596
but must understand that you have
to talk to Me

00:18:53.797 --> 00:19:00.460
in a way that is, you would talk
to Adi Shakti.

00:19:01.034 --> 00:19:03.535
Very important.

00:19:08.918 --> 00:19:15.819
Then how you behave is very important.
You should not be artificial,

00:19:16.020 --> 00:19:22.113
you should not be superficial, but best is
to put your hand on your heart,

00:19:22.314 --> 00:19:27.883
both the hands, and just try to feel it.

00:19:28.861 --> 00:19:32.332
Your Mother is Adi Shakti.

00:19:32.802 --> 00:19:39.291
She has created all this Universe, She
has created all this world,

00:19:40.007 --> 00:19:47.755
She is for your protection. Even
Shri Krishna could not protect

00:19:48.631 --> 00:19:54.026
Pandavas - they had to go in the forest,
they had to suffer.

00:19:54.227 --> 00:19:57.767
But not Sahaja Yogis.

00:19:58.706 --> 00:20:05.157
As soon as I come to know about your
problems, My attention can work out.

00:20:05.358 --> 00:20:09.480
Shri Rama Himself had to go to jungles.

00:20:09.681 --> 00:20:17.961
All this is given to you, this protection,
because you are seekers of truth,

00:20:18.162 --> 00:20:26.426
and the truth is that I am the Adi Shakti
incarnated.

00:20:33.420 --> 00:20:38.558
Once this truth becomes one with yourself

00:20:39.100 --> 00:20:44.590
there is nothing to fear, because
all the Deities know this fact,

00:20:44.798 --> 00:20:49.703
they know about this Incarnation very well.
They are all prepared for it,

00:20:49.904 --> 00:20:58.825
and they'll do anything to substantiate
your belief.

00:20:59.565 --> 00:21:04.851
In every way they are trying to give you
My photographs, in the sky, this, that,

00:21:05.052 --> 00:21:09.696
I mean all sorts of things. God knows what
they are going to do today.

00:21:10.158 --> 00:21:13.109
They are so anxious.

00:21:13.403 --> 00:21:17.654
They are behind the stage, before
the stage, all sides of the stage,

00:21:17.855 --> 00:21:23.484
listening to Me, feeling happy that I am
telling you the truth.

00:21:23.685 --> 00:21:30.905
But the way they recognize and the way
they act, they never disobey.

00:21:34.470 --> 00:21:37.880
If you behave in the same manner

00:21:38.081 --> 00:21:43.724
you are completely protected from all these
problems I have told you about.

00:21:45.385 --> 00:21:51.701
Now I won't say you shouldn't hate anyone,
you shouldn't do.., nothing of the kind.

00:21:55.084 --> 00:21:59.170
I wouldn't say you should not steal
something.

00:21:59.371 --> 00:22:05.778
I wouldn't say that you make money, don't
make money out of Sahaja Yoga, nothing.

00:22:05.979 --> 00:22:09.989
I don't even say don't drink, don't smoke,
I never said so.

00:22:10.190 --> 00:22:15.059
But automatically once you know whom
you are facing,

00:22:15.260 --> 00:22:19.460
in whose protection you are, automatically
you will do that.

00:22:19.661 --> 00:22:22.575
Automatically. You will have no fear.

00:22:22.776 --> 00:22:27.516
Once you have recognized you will have
no fear from anyone.

00:22:27.717 --> 00:22:35.325
And the more you show that recognition,
the more you realize it,

00:22:35.526 --> 00:22:41.522
you get higher and higher. Not only
spiritually,

00:22:41.723 --> 00:22:47.895
but every way - mentally, socially,
economically, politically.

00:22:50.714 --> 00:22:54.092
